{"tid":659783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷影休班警女友裙底 飛行隊總醫官判社服令","createTime":"2018-05-10T06:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T07:34:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b61ff5e317c08ed55602789aab39fa3e0d0a31f","tid":659783,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2065551/%e5%81%b7%e5%bd%b15%e5%a5%b3%e8%a3%99%e5%ba%95%20%e9%a3%9b%e8%a1%8c%e9%9a%8a%e7%b8%bd%e9%86%ab%e5%ae%98%e5%88%a4%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2065551%2F%25e5%2581%25b7%25e5%25bd%25b15%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e8%25a3%2599%25e5%25ba%2595%2520%25e9%25a3%259b%25e8%25a1%258c%25e9%259a%258a%25e7%25b8%25bd%25e9%2586%25ab%25e5%25ae%2598%25e5%2588%25a4%25e7%25a4%25be%25e6%259c%258d&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FEZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4ab356e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2065551/%e5%81%b7%e5%bd%b15%e5%a5%b3%e8%a3%99%e5%ba%95%20%e9%a3%9b%e8%a1%8c%e9%9a%8a%e7%b8%bd%e9%86%ab%e5%ae%98%e5%88%a4%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%8d</a><br />\n<br />\n飛行服務隊總飛行醫官胡永強，涉於前年9月17日在不同地方連環偷拍4名女子的裙底，當他在又一城的電梯上偷拍第5名女子時，被對方的休班警男友當場揭發，事後警方發現被告的手機記憶卡內載有於同日拍攝的5段裙底影片。<br />\n<br />\n被告胡永強（51歲）早前承認5項作出有違公德的行為罪，被還押逾一周後，昨被判180小時社會服務令，並須接受心理醫生輔導。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88035a752e63e52d5727cf0e86ea32ace9858983","tid":659783,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c387b112e1aeeeceb489a3a9c7bcbf3e3ca2f5f9","tid":659783,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"點都係同休班警有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}